title: Days of our Lives Fri, Aug 30, 2013
description:
Marlena tries to get the dirt on Kristen.



Roman refuses Marlena's request.



EJ warns Sami that she's making a mistake.


Sami backtracks and tells Trask to take her deal and shove it.



Eric has yet another upsetting dream then finds a matchbook from the hotel he stayed at.



Kristen accepts Brady's proposal.



Sonny makes things right with Gabi then finds a condom wrapper.



Will tells Nick he can't forgive him for putting the baby in danger.
